{"tid":1515453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［831遊行］警方向民陣發出反對通知書","createTime":"2019-08-29T07:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T10:06:06.000Z","uid":213379,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b87c0bcf16f2c46598335d2aa21fd49674265fef","tid":1515453,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:04:10.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警方向民陣發出反對通知書反對周六的831遊行。警方指由於近期示威活動衝突日趨暴力，擔心遊行會偏離原定路線，並對警察總部及中聯辦等有破壞行動，民陣表明會上訴。<br />\n<br />\n民陣計劃本周六遊行集會，要求撤回人大831決定、落實雙普選，以及重申反修例風波的五大訴求，當日朝十晚六在中環遮打花園舉行集會，下午三時遊行至中聯辦。<br />\n<br />\n民陣召集人岑子杰指收到警方通知，反對遊行並禁止集會。<br />\n<br />\n根據警方反對通知書指出，過去的示威活動後曾有示威者縱火、大範圍堵路，使用汽油彈、磚頭、鐵通等各類自製武器大規模破壞公物，破壞社會安寧、令他人受傷，而民陣申請的遊行集會地點十分接近禮賓府、中聯辦、終審法院、警察總部等。<br />\n<br />\n基於近期示威後發生嚴重衝突，而近日社會氣氛以及衝突日趨暴力，警方有理由相信今次遊行集會會偏離原定地點及路線，對上述的建築物進行破壞，嚴重威脅個人安全。<br />\n<br />\n警方又相信，行為不在民陣控制範圍內，民陣亦無能力確保參與者及市民人身安全，因此反對有關申請。<br />\n<br />\n民陣表明會上訴亦會與不同團體及政黨，商討如何在安全及合法下讓市民繼續行使遊行示威權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360885&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360885%26refer%3D&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=03d8eea1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360885%26refer%3D&h=8a850c70\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360885&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBxYHog.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBxYHog.jpg&h=eb4db28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打壓壓力越大 反抗力量越大<br />\n<br />\n我要真普選！<br />\n<br />\n831 三點 遮打花園集合！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502fe7b6a64e133f032ac8d6ec32654225551867","tid":1515453,"uid":273916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民陣電話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">用於傳短訊</span></span>, 不建議致電<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vD12Zp3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvD12Zp3.gif&h=f9a83f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcUsmkJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcUsmkJ.gif&h=2a4b8943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7Tdf8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP7Tdf8O.png&h=13ffde59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n831民陣大遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zJLGv0x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzJLGv0x.gif&h=e32fe2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZmfnY9d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZmfnY9d.gif&h=d6709f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n901 和你塞 13:00 <a href=\"http://見t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A6%8Bt.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=b0b3407d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">見t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRrZiocJRpRWN%2FM